Fstatus%2F1272682524884430848%3Fs%3D21%26fbclid%3DIwAR0N28MW7ZXHBFEEzcVvqzotM8vR1fb0uhr40FC55bnFqPdR6s3nOOz_dRM&h=9fa8287c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ozraeliavi/status/1272682524884430848?s=21&amp;fbclid=IwAR0N28MW7ZXHBFEEzcVvqzotM8vR1fb0uhr40FC55bnFqPdR6s3nOOz_dRM</a><br />\n<br />\n字幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sydneydaddy1/status/1272750704126377986?s=21&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ITu6if30wo2emSYvgKhabXbr-Q9_DCbMRN-cstqK3HwFJ01NJUIvhW-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsydneydaddy1%2Fstatus%2F1272750704126377986%3Fs%3D21%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ITu6if30wo2emSYvgKhabXbr-Q9_DCbMRN-cstqK3HwFJ01NJUIvhW-s&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=18f505c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsydneydaddy1%2Fstatus%2F1272750704126377986%3Fs%3D21%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ITu6if30wo2emSYvgKhabXbr-Q9_DCbMRN-cstqK3HwFJ01NJUIvhW-s&h=52ec85dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sydneydaddy1/status/1272750704126377986?s=21&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ITu6if30wo2emSYvgKhabXbr-Q9_DCbMRN-cstqK3HwFJ01NJUIvhW-s</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T23:07:31.000Z","msg":"民主黨建立各種制度限制管理國家，剝削特定團體<br />\n共和黨則不建立制度，將所有責任歸於個人，要求個人能力高，追求個人權利"},{"pid":"449c0a30ffc07ce63791031c77f435bf61d7ee08","tid":2067693,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T23:21:31.000Z","msg":"唯物佬認為物質獲得就ok，施捨夠就有票，你唔比票我，到時候就無人施捨你。你係需要人施捨蛇齋餅糉總需要嘅係唔係? 你係弱勢，係唔係? <br />\n若社會富裕未好似問題少D囉，社會結構係改唔到，所以好多黑人個成長氛圍一直都無變過。<br />\n當道德秩序係到，重視家庭，有信仰，個成長氛圍先唔同，就算窮亦會見到希望，否則下下都單親，遊蕩爛玩屌hi精，成區都係咁，咁係唔會變。"},{"pid":"35992156e60eac9a48468ffec2a070fa46689122","tid":2067693,"uid":321837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7625ff3971ea5ff00450a1fc42ea50f087f93243","tid":2067693,"uid":326037,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"75887d14695ea07cc8b5f7f346b85215931289bc","tid":2067693,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"任